Fever, aches, and chills? It could be #flu. 

It can be difficult to tell the difference between a cold and flu, but special tests done by your doctor during the first few days of illness can tell if you’re sick with #flu. 

Learn more: https://t.co/mRTOe2Exxm https://t.co/pzXJ7qVtP7
